Locale.Value:
Messenger
- You can drag apps and temporary tabs to adjust their position in the navigation bar, to make accessing what you need easier.
Docs
- New shapes are available, including cubes, right triangles, components, and more.
- The buttons on the board toolbar can be rearranged to suit your specific needs.
- Use search to quickly find the text you need in a board, no matter how much content it contains.
Base
- The new email field in Base validates email formats, ensuring data accuracy.
Email
- Set the priority level of an email when composing it. This helps recipients decide which emails to respond to first.
- Request a read receipt from recipients. When they open your email, they'll be asked to confirm they've read. This helps you know whether your email has been read.

即时消息
- 轻松拖拽即可对导航栏的内容进行位置调整，排列更有序，查看更方便
云文档
- 画板新图形上线，你可以在画板里插入立方体、直角三角形、组件等更多种图形
- 支持自定义画板工具栏的按钮顺序，你可以按自己的使用习惯将常用按钮放在前面展示
- 支持在画板中搜索内容，画板内容再多也无需担心找不到需要的内容
多维表格
- 多维表格新增 Email 字段，并支持校验邮箱格式，满足更多场景更多需求
邮箱
- 发送或回复邮件时，你可以为邮件设置优先级标识，提醒收件人及时处理邮件信息
- 写邮件时可开启“已读回执”，收件人阅读邮件时会被询问“是否发送回执”，确认发送后，发件人将收到一条回执消息，提示该邮件已被查看，方便你了解邮件阅读情况
